spec_data.Name: remctl-devel
spec_data.Description:
remctl implements a client/server protocol for running single commands
on a remote host using Kerberos v5 authentication. If you want to develop
programs which use remctl's libraries, you need to install this package.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sat 05 Aug 2017 11:43:46 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Development files needed to compile C programs against remctl
